tedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T14:27:13.000Z","msg":"用辣椒水殺蟲水之類噴眼可唔可以擊退佢地？<br />\n有咩基本防具要戴？"},{"pid":"4a375e9e6f3198e677d8bfc2800f4b391c1933e1","tid":1361742,"uid":53840,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T14:28:49.000Z","msg":"推<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">集中五大訴求<br />\n1.全面撤回逃犯條例<br />\n2.撤銷暴動定性<br />\n3.釋放被捕義士並承諾永不追究<br />\n4.全面實行雙普選<br />\n5.成立獨立調查委員會追究黑警責任(包括警黑勾結元朗恐襲)</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\">7.27 支持元朗居民,反黑鄉</div></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\"><br />\n兄弟爬山 各自努力 齊上齊落<br />\n不分化 不篤灰 不割蓆 不譴責 不撤不散<br />\n提防 三毛 五毛</div></span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"1a65fa4181ca18da0dabda328f74b072f2413478","tid":1361742,"uid":282350,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"af2fcda2edc931ba3a9bf57da0370fc6205263c5","tid":1361742,"uid":55874,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T14:27:13.000Z","msg":"用辣椒水殺蟲水之類噴眼可唔可以擊退佢地？<br />\n有咩基本防具要戴？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T14:37:39.000Z","msg":"噴霧絕對係自保好工具，但要小心誤中自己人<br />\n如果防具我會比較推薦背囊放毛公仔或大量毛巾，不過記得單邊咁揹，唔好上晒兩邊膊"},{"pid":"3f489799d2b9913afd2611434d793e1b7b15c139","tid":1361742,"uid":282350,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T15:23:47.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"0cbf7d0b812ab61cbadf28ce8b5b1afbcac780f2","tid":1361742,"uid":86277,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T15:36:10.000Z","msg":"握拳嘅時候可以揸住嘅圓柱形嘅嘅，例如一卷銀仔咁，握拳會firm啲，又可以增加個mass，拳拳有力"},{"pid":"99beffdec8b658f9e577ccb73f49d92c30146b0c","tid":1361742,"uid":282350,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0cbf7d0b812ab61cbadf28ce8b5b1afbcac780f2","tid":1361742,"uid":86277,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T15:36:10.000Z","msg":"握拳嘅時候可以揸住嘅圓柱形嘅嘅，例如一卷銀仔咁，握拳會firm啲，又可以增加個mass，拳拳有力"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T15:45:05.000Z","msg":"哩個非常好既提議，但因為每個人手既大細唔同，所以要自行測試揸實乜野，提議有以下：<br />\n1，7仔打火機<br />\n2，電芯<br />\n3，一扎綿花棒<br />\n4，原子筆<br />\n其他自行發揮創作空間，最緊要就手，拎出街又合情合理合法。"},{"pid":"04a4dc54f6f7281bcde4a945cb58e03db0c37224","tid":1361742,"uid":71140,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T15:56:16.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"a7ec62ea558dc843f89e9553e6225f92c2975c23","tid":1361742,"uid":282350,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"04a4dc54f6f7281bcde4a945cb58e03db0c37224","tid":1361742,"uid":71140,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T15:56:16.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T15:59:12.000Z","msg":"希望所有手足都唔好白白被打"},{"pid":"6ab237447c62fd5efbc85877ff01ad4d40f3d993","tid":1361742,"uid":10070,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T15:59:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"047baab51dec07393d3c3051973f6744b7ba0302","tid":1361742,"uid":23663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T16:09:04.000Z","msg":"推 一膽二力三功夫"},{"pid":"0f2f585be154d49be53e7322a06d4eda544e5236","tid":1361742,"uid":282350,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"047baab51dec07393d3c3051973f6744b7ba0302","tid":1361742,"uid":23663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T16:09:04.000Z","msg":"推 一膽二力三功夫"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T16:18:10.000Z","msg":"唔可以白白被打"},{"pid":"4c9acc4cb08ec084ee8f7e7a4a9d8b728487d091","tid":1361742,"uid":213893,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T16:20:05.000Z","msg":"認同唔應該拘泥陣式"},{"pid":"a6f0c78e538cbfb42f8916f2e0571f93b6dd46d8","tid":1361742,"uid":282350,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4c9acc4cb08ec084ee8f7e7a4a9d8b728487d091","tid":1361742,"uid":213893,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T16:20:05.000Z","msg":"認同唔應該拘泥陣式"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T16:23:09.000Z","msg":"有操練有意識既，用陣式當然好，但係如果拉雜成軍，遇倒班本身就係打算打人唔係迫開你既，太執著陣式，好易害死前排"},{"pid":"84a6ed5033d6c5dd5c303c8f940d9b639a89d288","tid":1361742,"uid":282350,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T16:55:10.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"856d3383e271ca8c93fd6ca8cbe09217ddedf4b0","tid":1361742,"uid":282350,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T17:12:24.000Z","msg":"會打算入元朗既手足，唔該入黎望望"},{"pid":"272c927cfb39bbfd7885a2ca917cbf05201ff1e0","tid":1361742,"uid":282350,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T17:32:59.000Z","msg":"希望唔會出現，但如果真係不幸落單又遇上暴徒，仲要無路走，咁唯一既自救方法就係背貼牆，嘗試cool住一件埋黎做人質，迫對方陣營俾路你走。但哩個方法風險好高，落單的話，盡快搵番人群啦"},{"pid":"0a4882144a35e02c423da49489c96776b72bc3a9","tid":1361742,"uid":181727,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T17:46:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a2837995e8ffc0a4859fb654a7482b7b2d7dfb7e","tid":1361742,"uid":282350,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T17:51:05.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"7f231dca9f3cb897f1335ce35ae9e2163c2cfec6","tid":1361742,"uid":165619,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5c1796b5923c055e6689be22eacd0cef29a3e924","tid":1361742,"uid":282350,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"90386386dda46e2aa944295da24df8c248e6eee5","tid":1361742,"uid":165619,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T17:52:18.000Z","msg":"如果體形有差距，點處理好？<br />\n<br />\n另外 建議用勾拳 定直拳好？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T17:56:45.000Z","msg":"體型差距<br />\n1，唔夠對方高，打下巴啦，你夠狠踢下陰<br />\n2，唔夠對方大份，打眼，打喉嚨<br />\n一定係勾拳，一般無訓練過既直拳，根本破壞力好低"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T02:41:00.000Z","msg":"好人一生平安<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c6748e5cdd8f15fbe79e225aba8d90a67e71d762","tid":1361742,"uid":282350,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0